策的悬念时刻","target":"imgs/inline-01.png","line":35,"embedded":true},{"title":"一个人站在分岔路口的插画，一条路指向屏幕和AI界面，另一条路指向一枚硬币，风格简洁现代","target":"imgs/inline-02.png","line":89,"embedded":true},{"title":"一组对比插画：左侧是被多个推荐气泡包围的人显得信息过载，右侧是手持硬币的人显得清晰从容，风格统一","target":"imgs/inline-03.png","line":141,"embedded":true},{"title":"Reddit帖子讨论的抽象可视化：社区围绕硬币聚集，远处是发光的AI界面，形成对比，扁平风格","target":"imgs/inline-04.png","line":191,"embedded":true},{"title":"Catalyzing decisions: How a coin flip strengthens affective reactions","target":"https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC6693849/","line":271},{"title":"Heads or Tails: The Impact of a Coin Toss on Major Life Decisions","target":"https://gwern.net/doc/psychology/cognitive-bias/2020-levitt.pdf","line":273},{"title":"Don't Leave Your Decision to Chance, Flip a Coin","target":"https://www.psychologytoday.com/us/blog/time-travelling-apollo/201906/dont-leave-your-decision-chance-flip-coin","line":275},{"title":"From algorithm aversion to AI dependence: Deskilling, upskilling, and emerging addictions in the GenAI age","target":"https://myscp.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1002/arcp.70008","line":277},{"title":"When Autonomy Breaks: The Hidden Existential Risk of AI","target":"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00146-025-02397-5","line":279},{"title":"Algorithm Aversion","target":"https://thedecisionlab.com/reference-guide/psychology/algorithm-aversion","line":281},{"title":"AI Boss Effect Report","target":"https://www.resume-now.com/job-resources/careers/ai-boss-effect-report","line":283},{"title":"How People Use & Trust ChatGPT in 2025","target":"https://expresslegalfunding.com/chatgpt-study/","line":285},{"title":"A quarter of Gen Zers have followed ChatGPT's career advice","target":"https://fortune.com/2025/08/19/quarter-of-gen-z-have-followed-ai-chatgpt-career-advice-and-few-have-regrets/","line":287},{"title":"AI and the future of human decision-making","target":"https://www.deloitte.com/us/en/insights/topics/talent/human-capital-trends/2026/decision-making-with-ai.html","line":289}],"metadata":{"title":"硬币决策法击败AI：为什么越来越多人用抛硬币做决定","author":"GeekJourney","description":"当97%的人开始向AI求助人生决策时，Reddit上18000人却选择了抛硬币。这不是反智，而是人类在算法时代对自主判断力的本能捍卫。从心理学实验到社会现象，硬币决策法揭示了一个被忽视的真相：有些答案，只有你自己知道。","digest":"97%的人向AI求助人生决策，Reddit上18000人却选了抛硬币——这不是反智，是人类自主性最后的防线。","coverImage":"imgs/cover.png","styleMode":"deep-analysis","sourceType":"topic-research","structureFrame":"deep-analysis","disclosure":"本文由AI辅助研究和写作，基于公开学术论文、调查报告和社区数据。所有数据点均标注来源。人类提供了核心论点框架和编辑审核。"},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:📤 产出/公众号/2026-04/20260410-硬币决策法击败AI/article-formatted.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1mq17rc","at":1776485849627},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06071871,-0.00390712,0.01236933,-0.03461228,0.04951784,0.01608337,-0.02775097,0.04943545,0.0570187,-0.02688311,0.00160467,-0.01690069,0.02850214,0.02950712,0.03922662,0.03964937,0.0079601,-0.08496521,-0.02516154,-0.018276,0.16478123,-0.06922002,0.04704658,-0.11049226,0.00196615,0.00147662,-0.01822253,-0.04775176,-0.00346267,-0.15018326,-0.04086735,-0.02959608,0.09769842,0.02096493,0.04048777,-0.01192249,-0.04934203,0.02073171,-0.01826725,0.01602878,-0.00008327,-0.0090928,0.05257434,0.03827308,0.07274475,0.02808899,-0.02417666,-0.03697526,-0.03367171,-0.02792035,-0.01561463,-0.03479804,0.01293355,0.04205925,0.01179155,0.00332572,0.06010852,0.03526536,0.05110752,0.03669142,0.04702527,0.03904206,-0.21208976,0.05459573,0.03211104,-0.0227294,-0.0288058,-0.05238523,0.03297625,0.04999796,-0.03890806,0.00500304,-0.00261856,0.01630965,0.03308699,-0.02887991,0.03265285,-0.03766242,-0.02555322,-0.05847907,-0.01151013,0.0844662,0.00009736,-0.00098842,-0.01380453,0.02610548,0.02156117,-0.06156591,-0.0164054,-0.02935472,0.02436419,-0.02261749,0.04001899,0.04031244,-0.00441948,0.01992894,-0.01900156,0.02832769,-0.04882644,0.08536739,-0.04049521,0.00302976,0.01991173,-0.02772908,0.03612934,-0.0307627,0.00285965,-0.03696884,-0.02704619,0.